.ie \n(.g .ds Aq \(aq
.el .ds Aq '
.TH btctax-reconcile-match-self-transfers 1  btctax "btctax manual"
.SH NAME
match\-self\-transfers \- Match unreconciled inbound + outbound legs as self\-transfers (self\-transfer\-passthrough C3). With no \-\-in/\-\-out: PREVIEW the proposed pairs (read\-only). With \-\-in and \-\-out: confirm ONE pair (DROP for a same\-wallet passthrough, RELOCATE for a cross\-wallet transfer). NEVER automatic
.SH SYNOPSIS
\fBmatch\-self\-transfers\fR [\fB\-\-in\fR] [\fB\-\-out\fR] [\fB\-\-action\fR] [\fB\-\-dry\-run\fR] [\fB\-h\fR|\fB\-\-help\fR] 
.SH DESCRIPTION
Match unreconciled inbound + outbound legs as self\-transfers (self\-transfer\-passthrough C3). With no \-\-in/\-\-out: PREVIEW the proposed pairs (read\-only). With \-\-in and \-\-out: confirm ONE pair (DROP for a same\-wallet passthrough, RELOCATE for a cross\-wallet transfer). NEVER automatic
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
\fB\-\-in\fR \fI<IN_REF>\fR
Confirm this in\-leg (TransferIn eventref); requires \-\-out
.TP
\fB\-\-out\fR \fI<OUT_REF>\fR
Confirm this out\-leg (TransferOut eventref); requires \-\-in
.TP
\fB\-\-action\fR \fI<ACTION>\fR
Override the suggested action (else the proposal\*(Aqs topology\-derived action is used)
.br

.br
\fIPossible values:\fR
.RS 14
.IP \(bu 2
drop: Same\-wallet passthrough → SelfTransferPassthrough (both legs skipped, non\-taxable)
.IP \(bu 2
relocate: Cross\-wallet transfer → TransferLink (relocate the lots to the destination wallet)
.RE
.TP
\fB\-\-dry\-run\fR
Print the preview and exit without writing (conflicts with \-\-in/\-\-out)
.TP
\fB\-h\fR, \fB\-\-help\fR
Print help (see a summary with \*(Aq\-h\*(Aq)
